      • getMarkedPlayer

        public Player getMarkedPlayer()
        Gets the marked player. Returns a player object of this tile if this tile is marked. Returns null by default as long as no player marked this tile in the game.
        Returns:
        marked player object of this tile object

      • isMarked

        public boolean isMarked()
        Returns whether this tile is marked. Returns whether this tile is marked by returning true if the marked player object of this tile object is not null, otherwise it returns false.
        Returns:
        true if marked player object is not null, otherwise false
